[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":1781},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20221215\u002F2411869749\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20221215\u002F2411869749\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20221215\u002F2411869749\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20221215\u002F2411869749\u002F":1756,"related:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20221215\u002F2411869749\u002F":1765},"\u002Fen\u002Fnodejs\u002F2022\u002F12\u002F15\u002Fdiscord-bot-with-openai-gpt3\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":1739,"date":1740,"description":18,"extension":1741,"lang":1742,"meta":1743,"navigation":390,"path":1744,"readingMinutes":1745,"seo":1746,"standalone":1747,"stem":1748,"tags":1749,"tldr":1752,"updated":1753,"url":1754,"__hash__":1755},"content\u002FNodejs\u002F用-OpenAI-GPT-3-建立一個-Discord-聊天機器人.md","用 OpenAI GPT-3 建立一個 Discord 聊天機器人","2411869749",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":1725},"minimark",[11,15,19,38,41,44,47,63,66,70,80,87,90,96,99,105,112,115,121,124,130,133,139,142,148,151,154,162,165,168,174,177,183,186,189,195,200,203,206,209,252,255,281,302,305,308,311,314,319,322,584,587,618,633,636,655,682,886,896,902,905,909,926,1269,1272,1294,1303,1315,1564,1571,1577,1582,1586,1589,1597,1600,1609,1612,1618,1621,1624,1627,1630,1633,1640,1643,1646,1669,1672,1675,1678,1693,1702,1713,1721],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"這一篇將會來介紹如何使用 OpenAI GPT-3 來建立一個 Discord 聊天機器人，並且讓它可以回應我們的訊息，而且你會發現 Discord 非常適合拿來串 OpenAI，雖然主軸是以 GPT-3 為主，但是我的範例程式碼也有提供 GPT-3.5 的 Commit 給予參考唷~",[20,21,24],"callout",{"title":22,"type":23},"Warning","warning",[16,25,26,27,31,32,37],{},"請注意，本篇",[28,29,30],"strong",{},"必須自己申請 OpenAI Key","，申請流程可詳見",[33,34,36],"a",{"href":35},"\u002Fnodejs\u002F20221210\u002F1224824056\u002F#%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B-OpenAI-API","這一篇","文章",[12,39,40],{"id":40},"事前說明",[16,42,43],{},"這一篇將不會有過多的著墨說明 Node.js、Git、GitHub、npm 等等的基礎知識，因為如果包含這些的話這一篇內容可能會多。",[16,45,46],{},"但是如果你對於 npm 與 Git 指令不熟悉的話，這邊我倒是可以提供自己先前的一些文章給予參考",[48,49,50,57],"ul",{},[51,52,53],"li",{},[33,54,56],{"href":55},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20200921\u002F849819598\u002F","(8) 試著學 Hexo - 你應該懂基本的 npm 指令",[51,58,59],{},[33,60,62],{"href":61},"\u002Fgit\u002F20190615\u002F1148594701\u002F","基礎 Git 指令",[16,64,65],{},"當然結尾我也會附上範例程式碼的 GitHub 連結，到時候我也會針對 README 進行一些說明，方便你可以快速運作一個 Discord 機器人。",[12,67,69],{"id":68},"discord-準備動作","Discord 準備動作",[16,71,72,73,79],{},"首先第一個步驟是我們要先去建立一個 Discord 機器人，首先請你先到 ",[33,74,78],{"href":75,"rel":76},"https:\u002F\u002Fdiscord.com\u002Fdevelopers\u002Fapplications",[77],"nofollow","Discord Developer Portal"," 頁面點選 Application",[16,81,82],{},[83,84],"img",{"alt":85,"src":86},"Application","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002Fa0Od41t.png",[16,88,89],{},"然後點選 「New Application」",[16,91,92],{},[83,93],{"alt":94,"src":95},"New Application","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FaEa0M5F.png",[16,97,98],{},"接著會要求你輸入這個機器人的名稱，這邊我們就叫做「OpenAI GPT-3」吧",[16,100,101],{},[83,102],{"alt":103,"src":104},"OpenAI GPT-3","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FcFSnLzP.png",[20,106,109],{"title":107,"type":108},"Note","note",[16,110,111],{},"請注意，這個應用程式的名稱不是機器人的名稱，除此之外到時候這個應用程式名稱也會變成 Discord 伺服器的權限名稱，所以請記得要取一個好的名稱。",[16,113,114],{},"進到「OpenAI GPT-3」應用程式頁面後，我們要先去建立一個機器人，點選左邊的「Bot」",[16,116,117],{},[83,118],{"alt":119,"src":120},"Bot","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FbaUchls.png",[16,122,123],{},"然後再點右邊「Add Bot」",[16,125,126],{},[83,127],{"alt":128,"src":129},"Add Bot","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FvnpXA5Y.png",[16,131,132],{},"當你按下「Add Bot」後，Discord 會要求你確認是否要建立一個機器人，點選「Yes, do it!」",[16,134,135],{},[83,136],{"alt":137,"src":138},"Yes, do it!","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FN6LdkrN.png",[16,140,141],{},"接著下方就會出現你的機器人，這邊請你找到「Token」的欄位，並且按一下「Reset Token」",[16,143,144],{},[83,145],{"alt":146,"src":147},"Reset Token","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FA5iTEwZ.png",[16,149,150],{},"這時候你會取得一串 Token，這串 Token 就是你的機器人的 Token，請記得要把它記下來，因為之後我們會用到它。",[16,152,153],{},"請不要隨意將你的機器人 Token 分享給別人，因為這樣會讓別人可以控制你的機器人。",[16,155,156,157,161],{},"除此之外，這邊 ",[158,159,160],"code",{},"Username"," 將會是你的機器人的名稱，在最後的範例程式碼，我是把它叫做「妙麗·格蘭傑」就是了。",[16,163,164],{},"接著這邊有一件事情很重要，麻煩滾到下方一點的地方找到「Privileged Gateway Intents」，然後把「Message Content Intent」打開，這樣才能讓機器人可以接收到訊息唷！",[16,166,167],{},"接著呢？我們要去把這個機器人加入到我們的 Discord 伺服器中，點選左邊的「OAuth2」，然後再選「URL Generator」的方式（比較簡單）",[16,169,170],{},[83,171],{"alt":172,"src":173},"URL Generator","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FLtQioGX.png",[16,175,176],{},"進入後，請在左邊的「SCOPES」中勾選「bot」，然後在「BOT PERMISSIONS」中勾選「Send Messages」",[16,178,179],{},[83,180],{"alt":181,"src":182},"Send Messages","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FeiUZwyz.png",[16,184,185],{},"由於我們只是要讓機器人可以回應我們的訊息，所以我們只勾選「Send Messages」，如果你想要讓機器人可以做更多事情，可以再斟酌一下要勾選哪些權限。",[16,187,188],{},"接著下方你應該就會看到一塊「Generated URL」的區塊，將那一串 URL 複製下來並貼到瀏覽器的網址列上，然後按下 Enter，基本上你應該就會看到選擇要將機器人加入到哪個伺服器的畫面，選擇好你的伺服器後就大膽的把它加入吧！",[16,190,191],{},[83,192],{"alt":193,"src":194},"Add to Bot","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FePRXynz.png",[16,196,197],{},[83,198],{"alt":193,"src":199},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FpbMp7A7.png",[16,201,202],{},"這樣子你的機器人就會進入到你的伺服器了，那麼到這邊為止，我們基本的 Discord 機器人算是建立完成了。",[12,204,205],{"id":205},"建立專案環境",[16,207,208],{},"首先請你先建立一個資料夾，例如...叫做「discord-bot」，然後當然就是初始化這個專案，所以我這邊就快速貼上相關的指令：",[210,211,216],"pre",{"className":212,"code":213,"language":214,"meta":215,"style":215},"language-bash shiki shiki-themes github-light github-light github-dark-high-contrast","mkdir discord-bot\ncd discord-bot\nnpm init -y\n","bash","",[158,217,218,231,240],{"__ignoreMap":215},[219,220,223,227],"span",{"class":221,"line":222},"line",1,[219,224,226],{"class":225},"smYoP","mkdir",[219,228,230],{"class":229},"sWayO"," discord-bot\n",[219,232,234,238],{"class":221,"line":233},2,[219,235,237],{"class":236},"stw71","cd",[219,239,230],{"class":229},[219,241,243,246,249],{"class":221,"line":242},3,[219,244,245],{"class":225},"npm",[219,247,248],{"class":229}," init",[219,250,251],{"class":236}," -y\n",[16,253,254],{},"接著我們要來安裝一些我們會使用到的套件",[48,256,257,265,273],{},[51,258,259,260],{},"dotenv\n",[48,261,262],{},[51,263,264],{},"用來讀取 .env 檔案",[51,266,267,268],{},"discord.js\n",[48,269,270],{},[51,271,272],{},"用來操作 Discord 的 套件",[51,274,275,276],{},"openai\n",[48,277,278],{},[51,279,280],{},"用來操作 OpenAI GPT-3 的 套件",[210,282,284],{"className":212,"code":283,"language":214,"meta":215,"style":215},"npm install dotenv discord.js openai\n",[158,285,286],{"__ignoreMap":215},[219,287,288,290,293,296,299],{"class":221,"line":222},[219,289,245],{"class":225},[219,291,292],{"class":229}," install",[219,294,295],{"class":229}," dotenv",[219,297,298],{"class":229}," discord.js",[219,300,301],{"class":229}," openai\n",[16,303,304],{},"接著在專案根目錄建立一個「index.js」的檔案，因為接下來我們會開始在這一個檔案內撰寫我們的機器人程式碼。",[16,306,307],{},"（你也可以考慮加入 ESLint 管理你的程式碼品質唷）",[12,309,310],{"id":310},"撰寫程式碼",[16,312,313],{},"終於到了撰寫程式碼的環節了，那麼這邊可能不會每一行都說明，但會盡可能的簡單一點，讓你可以盡可能做出一個自己的機器人。",[315,316,318],"h3",{"id":317},"discord-機器人","Discord 機器人",[16,320,321],{},"首先，先讓我們撰寫 Discord 的機器人程式碼，那麼在官方 npm 上面，我們可以找到 Discord.js 的使用方式",[210,323,327],{"className":324,"code":325,"language":326,"meta":215,"style":215},"language-js shiki shiki-themes github-light github-light github-dark-high-contrast","const { Client, GatewayIntentBits } = require('discord.js');\nconst client = new Client({ intents: [GatewayIntentBits.Guilds] });\n\nclient.on('ready', () => {\n  console.log(`Logged in as ${client.user.tag}!`);\n});\n\nclient.on('interactionCreate', async interaction => {\n  if (!interaction.isChatInputCommand()) return;\n\n  if (interaction.commandName === 'ping') {\n    await interaction.reply('Pong!');\n  }\n});\n\nclient.login(TOKEN);\n","js",[158,328,329,367,386,392,415,448,454,459,485,512,517,534,553,559,564,569],{"__ignoreMap":215},[219,330,331,335,339,342,345,348,351,354,358,361,364],{"class":221,"line":222},[219,332,334],{"class":333},"sOudu","const",[219,336,338],{"class":337},"s8XSl"," { ",[219,340,341],{"class":236},"Client",[219,343,344],{"class":337},", ",[219,346,347],{"class":236},"GatewayIntentBits",[219,349,350],{"class":337}," } ",[219,352,353],{"class":333},"=",[219,355,357],{"class":356},"scAaK"," require",[219,359,360],{"class":337},"(",[219,362,363],{"class":229},"'discord.js'",[219,365,366],{"class":337},");\n",[219,368,369,371,374,377,380,383],{"class":221,"line":233},[219,370,334],{"class":333},[219,372,373],{"class":236}," client",[219,375,376],{"class":333}," =",[219,378,379],{"class":333}," new",[219,381,382],{"class":356}," Client",[219,384,385],{"class":337},"({ intents: [GatewayIntentBits.Guilds] });\n",[219,387,388],{"class":221,"line":242},[219,389,391],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":390},true,"\n",[219,393,395,398,401,403,406,409,412],{"class":221,"line":394},4,[219,396,397],{"class":337},"client.",[219,399,400],{"class":356},"on",[219,402,360],{"class":337},[219,404,405],{"class":229},"'ready'",[219,407,408],{"class":337},", () ",[219,410,411],{"class":333},"=>",[219,413,414],{"class":337}," {\n",[219,416,418,421,424,426,429,432,435,438,440,443,446],{"class":221,"line":417},5,[219,419,420],{"class":337},"  console.",[219,422,423],{"class":356},"log",[219,425,360],{"class":337},[219,427,428],{"class":229},"`Logged in as ${",[219,430,431],{"class":337},"client",[219,433,434],{"class":229},".",[219,436,437],{"class":337},"user",[219,439,434],{"class":229},[219,441,442],{"class":337},"tag",[219,444,445],{"class":229},"}!`",[219,447,366],{"class":337},[219,449,451],{"class":221,"line":450},6,[219,452,453],{"class":337},"});\n",[219,455,457],{"class":221,"line":456},7,[219,458,391],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":390},[219,460,462,464,466,468,471,473,476,480,483],{"class":221,"line":461},8,[219,463,397],{"class":337},[219,465,400],{"class":356},[219,467,360],{"class":337},[219,469,470],{"class":229},"'interactionCreate'",[219,472,344],{"class":337},[219,474,475],{"class":333},"async",[219,477,479],{"class":478},"syBk-"," interaction",[219,481,482],{"class":333}," =>",[219,484,414],{"class":337},[219,486,488,491,494,497,500,503,506,509],{"class":221,"line":487},9,[219,489,490],{"class":